label: Pubic symphysis morphological stage value specification
editor preferred term: Pubic symphysis morphological stage value specification
definition: A categorical value specification defining an ordinal scale of stages in the degradation of the pubic symphysis.
definition source: Felix Engel

label: Pubic symphysis morphological stage item sorting
definition: A label sorting specification about the position of a category label within the ordinal scale defined by some 'Pubic symphysis morphological stage value specification'.
definition source: Felix Engel
